(1344, 270, 'bloque_acerca_de_mi_texto', 'I am a Mexican freelance children\'s book illustrator. As a graduate of Animation and digital arts, I am deeply passionate about storytelling through images and diving into the wonderful world of children\'s books. Throughout my career, I have had the opportunity to collaborate with various Mexican brands, where I have showcased my versatility as a designer, illustrator, and content creator.\r\n\r\nMy goal is to transport you through my illustrations to a cozy universe filled with joy. I love bringing endearing characters to life and creating an atmosphere that transports you into a peaceful, magical world.'),
