(220, 2, '2023-09-06 16:53:00', '2023-09-06 16:53:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A series I did for a project titled \"Here I am: women in art history\" which I developed as part of my art history course at University. The objective of this project is to retrieve spaces and recognition that was taken away from women throughout art history. The artists portrayed are Remedios Varo, Sofonisba Anguissola and Mary Cassat respectively.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":221,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_0225-1-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-221\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":222,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_0224-1-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-222\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":223,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_0223-1-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-223\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Here I am... Women in art history - chapter book illustrations', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'here-i-am-women-in-art-history', '', '', '2024-06-14 17:13:55', '2024-06-14 17:13:55', '', 0, 'https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/?p=220', 0, 'post', '', 0),
