(244, 2, '2023-09-19 18:26:38', '2023-09-19 18:26:38', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I created a mini story that reminds us how bright and important friendship is when the wheather (or life) is a little cloudy. This illustrations are created as if they are part of an illustrated children\'s book, taking into account composition and text placement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":171,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Pagina-1-y-2-eng-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":173,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Pagina-3-y-4-eng-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-173\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Friendship is like sunshine - pages', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'friendship-is-like-sunshine-2', '', '', '2024-06-14 16:47:38', '2024-06-14 16:47:38', '', 0, 'https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/?p=244', 0, 'post', '', 0),
