(247, 2, '2023-09-19 18:30:11', '2023-09-19 18:30:11', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As I am entering a new stage in my life, I wanted to take a step back and look inside, that´s how this illustration was born. Having a conversation with my younger self, who I want to make proud. I wanted to portray the conection that we share with our inner child, and how important it is to nurture and honor that relationship. Made in Procreate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":190,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_4118-1-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Cute illustration with a kid in a garden\" class=\"wp-image-190\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'We\'re on our own, kid - illustration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'were-on-our-own-kid', '', '', '2024-06-14 16:58:06', '2024-06-14 16:58:06', '', 0, 'https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/?p=247', 0, 'post', '', 0);
