(256, 2, '2024-02-17 21:28:04', '2024-02-17 21:28:04', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is something about trees that invites everyone to gather around them, or below them, or in them! A tree is something that feels familiar and magical at the same time, it is at the same time a living being and a place, a place where you can play, discover, read and make new friends! That\'s what I wanted to capture with this cover mockup, the sense of community and wonder that can be found only under the shade of a tree. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":258,\"width\":\"840px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IMG_9256-819x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-258\" style=\"width:840px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":257,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IMG_9257-819x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-257\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'A place for everyone - cover mockup', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-place-for-everyone-cover-mockup', '', '', '2024-02-17 21:28:04', '2024-02-17 21:28:04', '', 0, 'https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/?p=256', 0, 'post', '', 0),
