(264, 2, '2024-05-03 17:58:02', '2024-05-03 17:58:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve always loved the word \"Grasshopper\", I find it so fun and interesting, so I decided to take it to its most literal sense for this cover! I played with different mediums to achieve the result I wanted, mixing paper art with gouache painting and digital touches. Grasshoppers always remind me of those times when I would play with my siblings in the grassland, almost completely covered by them, I felt like a little grasshopper. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":272,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/IMG_1230-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-272\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":266,\"width\":\"840px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/IMG_7446-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-266\" style=\"width:840px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":267,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/IMG_7458-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-267\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Grasshoppers - cover', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'grasshoppers', '', '', '2024-05-28 18:04:32', '2024-05-28 18:04:32', '', 0, 'https://marianagutierrezillustration.com/?p=264', 0, 'post', '', 0),
